org.logicmill.util.concurrent

Interface ConcurrentHashMap.Buildable

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    ConcurrentHashMap.LoadFactorSpec, ConcurrentHashMap.MapConfigBuilder, ConcurrentHashMap.SegCountSpec
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    ConcurrentHashMap.MapConfigBuilderImpl
    Enclosing class:
    ConcurrentHashMap<K,V>

    public static interface ConcurrentHashMap.Buildable
    An object returned by withLoadFactor(). This interface constrains operations to ensure proper ordering of invocations in a MapConfig chain, supporting the build() method that terminates the chain.
    Author:
    edgeofmagic
